piwik (2.4.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.4.0
  * Better Data Insights. Show me what's increased and decreased, movers
    and shakers (beta) (Closes: #57)
  * Remove Zeitgeist theme from Piwik and support only Morpheus (Closes:
    #5222)
  * Tracking API: major performance improvements with Transactions, when
    using Bulk Tracking (Closes: #5275)
  * Referrers overview: report labels should show more characters before
    truncation (Closes: #5394)
  * Log Analytics: several performance improvements (Closes: #5314)
  * New setting: enable Left Menu mode (Closes: #5212)
  * LibreJS compatibility for piwik.js: free/libre license notice
    (Closes: #3770)
  * Simplify / improve top menu (Closes: #5192)
  * Enable DevicesDetection plugin by default (Closes: #5329)
  * Developers: provide a simpler ScheduledTasks API (Closes: #5301)
  * Developers: new hooks in Login: 'Login.authenticate',
    'Login.authenticate.successful' (Closes: #5331)
  * Developers: new hook Live.makeNewVisitorObject for plugins to
    customise Visitor object (Closes: #5360)
  * Switching metrics in row evolution view doesn't work after changing
    report timespan (Closes: #5303)
  * New parameters for the core:archive console command for power users
    (Closes: #5396)
  * Change piwik URL to builds.piwik.org/piwik-latest.zip (Closes:
    #4455)
  * Row Evolution shows wrong data when directory and file with
    identical names exist at same level (Closes: #4363)
  * PiwikTracker PHP client: when bulk tracking, Custom variables are
    now reset after each request (Closes: #5291)
  * php console core:update -> issue using Piwik 2.3.0 (Closes: #5306)
  * Calculation All Websites dashboard wrong (Closes: #5320)
  * DataTable footer drawer does not expand when clicked (Closes: #5332)
  * When a custom date range is requested, the timezone of the requested
    website may be ignored (Closes: #5356)
  * When running piwik proxy php to hide footprint, IP address is not
    set correctly when the website being tracked is behind proxy
    (Closes: #2900)
  * When 10 widgets request the same site + date + segment at once,
    check it is archived only once (Closes: #4918)
  * make core:archive command compatibile with HHVM (Closes: #5263)
  * htaccess should help apache serve HTML files properly with:
    AddHandler text/html .html (Closes: #5266)
  * Include Meta tag IE=edge for best security practises (Closes: #5282)
  * Ensure all directories in plugins/ (Closes: #5311)
  * New system check to alert user when session.auto_start = 1 (Closes:
    #5344)
  * Limits ability of different Piwik instances to cross-match users
    (privacy) (Closes: #5366)
  * Detect requests from iTunes (Closes: #4017)
  * Support for user-agent string from AFNetworking library (iOS)
    (Closes: #5025)
  * Cron core:archive: make sure the PHP cli binary is at least 5.3.2
    (Closes: #5343)
  * Piwik should work as expected when PHP setting session.hash_function
    has non default value (Closes: #5371)
  * Make "Site Search" on "All Websites Dashboard" case-insensitive
    (Closes: #5382)
  * piwik.js: new function setCustomRequestProcessing() to let you edit
    the tracking request before it is sent (Closes: #5384)
  * Piwik.js: ability to register plugins to execute logic when a
    request is sent (Closes: #5393)
  * New config setting: set the Scheduled report emails Reply-to field
    to Email and Alias name of report creator (Closes: #5387)
  * Nightingale Media Player not detected correctly (Closes: #4870)
  * API: get PageUrl returns same results for several day (Closes:
    #4872)
  * Error when running cron:archive: Response was 'Console ToolUsage:
    [options] command.... (Closes: #5007)
  * Website dropdown no longer appears (Closes: #5213)
  * German translation incomplete in version 2.3.0 (Closes: #5240)
  * Visitor/locations: Map region selector to narrow (Closes: #5243)
  * Long Segment names break segment listing layout (Closes: #5247)
  * Error in "Database Usage" usage ... (Closes: #5253)
  * import_logs give a IOError: [Errno 29] Illegal seek when receiving
    log from pipe (Closes: #5254)
  * IIS: web.config should allow to server HTM, HTML and SVG files.
    (Closes: #5255)
  * Visitor Generator not working from console (Closes: #5256)
  * Not well testable php class method URL::redirectToUrl($url) (Closes:
    #5262)
  * 2.3.0: Visitors in Real-time widget, incorrect page title display
    (Closes: #5268)
  * invalidateArchivedReports $dates issue (Closes: #5281)
  * Remove plugins/Zeitgeist/ (Closes: #5297)
  * Incorrect domain age reported (Closes: #5322)
  * Warning: syntax error, unexpected $end, expecting '}' in
    config.ini.php in libs/upgradephp/upgrade.php (Closes: #5349)
  * Dropping outdated archives can timeout on huge Piwik instances
    (Closes: #5354)
  * Auto archiving: all websites should be archived at least once per
    day (Closes: #5358)
  * DBStats: Call to a member function getColumn() on a non-object in
    core/DataTable/Filter/ColumnCallbackAddColumnQuotient (Closes:
    #5370)
  * getVisitorProfilePopup: error on empty data (Closes: #5383)
  * FatalError - subDay() in API.php (Closes: #5388)
  * Support user agents of PIM clients (calendar, email) and feed
    readers (RSS, Atom) (Closes: #3651)
  * hardcoded user in permission error (Closes: #5339)

