    generate auto suggested values (Closes: #4253)
  * "Custom segment" is displayed instead of real name (Closes: #5053)
  * PHP Tracker: new method setForceNewVisit() to force creation of a
    new visit (Closes: #5123)
  * Remember detailed visitor log 'Rows to display' (Closes: #5162)
  * Configurable "Rows to display" limit. (Closes: #5188)
  * Use consistent fonts and colors in new Morpheus theme CSS/less
    (Closes: #4457)
  * Widget selector sometimes not displayed in dashboard (firefox)
    (Closes: #5227)
  * Improvements for custom events in tables like visitor log (Closes:
    #5189)
  * Custom logo: transparency channel replaced with black color (Closes:
    #5207)
  * sum_daily_nb_uniq_visitors calculations incorrect for some ranges in
    many API methods (Closes: #4377)
  * Generated .htaccess in plugins folder breaks all plugins (Closes:
    #4499)
  * When adding new annotation calendar not visible (Closes: #4510)
  * Real time map: west coast visitors are not clickable (Closes: #4613)
  * Apostrophes (and maybe other special characters) are shown encoded
    in page tooltip (Closes: #4749)
  * Changes to Sessions to improve compatibility, Browser Session was
    lost on PHP 5.5 (Closes: #4806)
  * Tooltip is unreadable (Closes: #5000)
  * MultiSites: On first login,the currencies of the websites aren't
    recognized correctly (Closes: #5006)
  * showing ' HTML code of single quote character instead of ' symbol in
    page titles (Closes: #5026)
  * procfs needed by process component (Closes: #5041)
  * datatable footer of the map widget is displayed only when the widget
    is maximized (Closes: #5047)
  * Make tracking several site IDs easier to users implementing Piwik
    using Asynchronous javascript (Closes: #5049)
  * in Visitors - Overview, Action metrics not displayed when report
    purge is enabled (Closes: #5054)
  * Logo appears stretched and pixelated on IE10+ (Closes: #5100)
  * All Websites is a blank page (Closes: #5102)
  * Plugins may not be installed correctly in some cases (Closes: #5115)
  * Dashboard "Length of Visits" widget, Pie Chart incorrect %
    calculation (Closes: #5116)
  * Set Base URL used in the AJAX request to ? instead of index.php?
    (Closes: #5127)
  * Image tracker displays wrong code: idSite= instead but idsite=
    should be used (Closes: #5131)
  * Calling API with serialize=0, get: Array to string conversion in
